[
  {
    "startTime": 1.6,
    "endTime": 10.6,
    "text": "I'm scared that my time with you will be cut short. No more stakeouts or drinks after a long shift or midnight calls when you've had a breakthrough in a case."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.7,
    "endTime": 20.7,
    "text": "I've always had this image of us in our 90s hunting down criminals at the retirement home, but I guess that was just a dumb fantasy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.8,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "Jake, are you crying?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.1,
    "endTime": 26.3,
    "text": "No.... Yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.4,
    "endTime": 28.4,
    "text": "In the face of crisis..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.5,
    "endTime": 31.4,
    "text": "I seem to have sent a digital phallus portrait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.5,
    "endTime": 33.3,
    "text": "Oh, no! You sent him a [bleep] pic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.3,
    "endTime": 34.199999999999996,
    "text": "Chaos..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.3,
    "endTime": 36.4,
    "text": "The other district sent us their Hitchcock-and-Scullys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.5,
    "endTime": 37.2,
    "text": "Dear God!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.4,
    "endTime": 39.199999999999996,
    "text": "- Nine-Nine!  - Nine-Nine!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.2,
    "endTime": 40.800000000000004,
    "text": "And childcare."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.8,
    "endTime": 42.599999999999994,
    "text": "- What are you doing here?  - What are you doing here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.6,
    "endTime": 44.878,
    "text": "(Both) You're supposed to be getting Matt from daycare!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.8,
    "endTime": 47.699999999999996,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.7,
    "endTime": 49.400000000000006,
    "text": "One team will rise..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.5,
    "endTime": 53.6,
    "text": "This workplace is my family. Was that not clear? Holt is my dad, you're my mean older sister, Amy's my mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.7,
    "endTime": 54.788000000000004,
    "text": "- What?!  - What? What did I say?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.788,
    "endTime": 55.699999999999996,
    "text": "For one..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.8,
    "endTime": 56.5,
    "text": "Hot damn!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.5,
    "endTime": 57.2,
    "text": "Last..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.3,
    "endTime": 58.099999999999994,
    "text": "(Laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.2,
    "endTime": 59.5,
    "text": "Ride."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.5,
    "endTime": 62.6,
    "text": "\"It is\", as Peralta would say, \"no big whoop.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.7,
    "endTime": 65.0,
    "text": "I actually don't pronounce the \"H\" in \"whoop\"."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "Let's ride!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.8,
    "endTime": 70.7,
    "text": "My edibles just kicked in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.7,
    "endTime": 71.8,
    "text": "Aah! Aah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.9,
    "endTime": 73.5,
    "text": "(Alarm blaring) Whoo, boy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.5,
    "endTime": 75.4,
    "text": "Pop, pop, pop, pop, pop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.4,
    "endTime": 76.60000000000001,
    "text": "(Dog growls)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.6,
    "endTime": 77.69999999999999,
    "text": "Witness the end..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.7,
    "endTime": 79.7,
    "text": "Oh, dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.7,
    "endTime": 80.5,
    "text": "Whoo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.5,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "Of the Nine-Nine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.0,
    "endTime": 88.1,
    "text": "Well, it seems I was wrong. So \"whoop\" is big after all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.1,
    "endTime": 91.19999999999999,
    "text": "Again, though, there's -- there's no \"H\" in \"whoop.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.2,
    "endTime": 93.7,
    "text": "- 'W'hoop. - W'h'oop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.7,
    "endTime": 95.5,
    "text": "Am I crazy? How do you say it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.5,
    "endTime": 97.9,
    "text": "- I say \"hu-woop.\" - Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.9,
    "endTime": 104.471,
    "text": "\"Brooklyn Nine-Nine.\" The final season premiers August 12th on NBC, and watch all past seasons on Peacock."
  }
]